PORT=3000
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here
PROFILE_PROMPT="Make this look like a real iPhone front-camera selfie for a social media profile pic. Keep the person's identity, face, and features EXACTLY the same.\n\nRULES:\n- The person must have a natural relaxed expression — slight smile, or smirk, or mid-laugh, or playful look. NEVER a blank neutral dead stare.\n- Head slightly tilted to one side. Shoulders NOT perfectly square — one shoulder slightly higher or turned. Natural body language like a real person, not a mannequin.\n- Face placed off-center in the frame (left third or right third). NOT centered.\n- Camera angle: randomly vary — selfie from slightly above, or from below chin level, or 3/4 side angle from left, or 3/4 from right, or mirror selfie. Pick a different one each time. NEVER straight-on centered.\n- Background: a random real-life location — mall, concert, rooftop, house party, beach, restaurant, nightclub, gym, stadium, street food market, car, kitchen, balcony, wedding, festival, arcade, karaoke, hotel room, ski trip, aquarium, cinema. Pick ONE randomly. Include real environmental details (people, signs, lights, furniture). NO parks, NO cafés as default.\n- NO depth of field blur. Background mostly in focus like a real front camera. NOT portrait mode.\n- Ambient lighting ONLY from the environment. No studio light, no ring light, no flash. Uneven or imperfect lighting is good.\n- DO NOT smooth or retouch skin. Keep ALL pores, texture, blemishes, under-eye shadows, oily shine. The skin must look like real unedited skin, not airbrushed.\n- Square 1:1 crop. The photo must look like an unedited spontaneous selfie straight from camera roll — not AI generated, not posed, not retouched."
JOB_TTL_MS=3600000
MAX_FILE_SIZE_MB=50
FRAME_RATE=2
NUM_FRAMES=3
